      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GINGERS SISTER (3) won narrowly two back before rising in trip last time out and never looking likely. Back to 1500m today looks a good move and Campbell hops back on board after guiding her to victory two back. Likely to get back in the run but she can mow them down to score. THINK LIKA WINNER (5) never featured back in trip last time out after a better run here two starts ago. Whiting returns to the saddle and this looks an easier race on paper to what he contested last time out. Ticks some boxes and can give himself every chance. WIN TO RETIRE (7) didn't see out the extra journey most recently after a strong run over the mile here two back. The claim of Riordan comes in handy and she's likely to be prominent from the good draw. Can bounce back in a big way. ETERNALLY YOURS (2) draws nicely and can improve with the fresh run under his belt. DIABLO LAD (1) looks an improver stepping out in distance.",
